          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "I go to the iStore to replace my broken AirPods. Then I get the hell out of there. I test our the new earphones in the car and am so surprised at how good the audio quality and noise cancellation is. I treat myself to an ice cream and coffee before hitting the N3. ",
