    "type": "paragraph",
    "paragraph": {
      "rich_text": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": {
            "content": "As I arrive back Kassie calls me. I sit on the swing bench by my campsite and we have a lovely catchup. She tells me about her knew job that is going to relocate her to Zanzibar - it’s a beautiful opportunity and I’m so proud of her. I setup the car for sleeping, order a burger and have a shower.",
            "link": null
          },
          "annotations": {
